First, go immediately to Casters Realm.  There is all types of information there on Spell Research.<br>
<br>
1 - There is a book that you need that is a 4 slot combine element, I forget the name but its available at all chanter guilds somewhere.<br>
<br>
2 - You will need pages they are numbered and vary by name on level.  You will need to combine 2 pages or 1/2 pages to make a spell.<br>
<br>
3 - There are ways to raise your research through &quot;quests&quot;.  This is basically farming items for combines that raise your research skill.  I have never done them.<br>
<br>
Again, start with Casters Realm.<br>
