<br>
2 - Pages and not words! These do normally drop from old world and kunark mobs of same level and up to 4 levels above the spell level you are gathering pages for. Some pages are faded, but can be restored by combining them alone in the book above.<br>
<br>
3 - Forget about the research quests, its so much not worth it. Its ALOT faster and cheaper to just buy the pages from vendors or even from players compared to doing the quests and the chance of a skillup seems to be the same with quests as with real combines. <p><br>
